title: GTA Online
headline: GTA Online
subtitle: 2X GTA$ on Bail Office Staff Income
content:
The Bail Office’s staff is here to aid in your bounty hunting efforts and also help pad your pockets. Collect 2X GTA$ on Bail Office Staff Income through December 9.

Purchase Agent Upgrades from Maze Bank Foreclosures at 40% off, then pay them a visit at their desks inside your Bail Office to put 'em to work.
